{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-049","title":"Sentence 49","sectionId":"sentences-041","sectionTitle":"Sentence 41-50","pageStart":329,"pageEnd":334,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":41,"duplicateEntryCount":5,"pages":[{"number":329,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 49"},{"type":"definition","text":"A mountain range may emerge and gradually split a population of"},{"type":"text","text":"organisms that can inhabit only lowland lakes; certain fish populations"},{"type":"text","text":"might become isolated in this way."},{"type":"text","text":"一条山脉可能会出现，并逐渐隔绝一个仅在低地湖泊栖息的生"},{"type":"text","text":"物种群，某些鱼群可能会通过这种方式被隔离。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句是由分号连接的两个并列分句。第一个分句的主干是A"},{"type":"text","text":"mountain range may emerge and split a population，定语从句that can"},{"type":"text","text":"inhabit only lowland lakes修饰organisms；第二个分句的主干是"},{"type":"text","text":"Populations might become isolated。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"range /reɪndʒ/ n. 范围；山脉","headword":"range"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 本身为词根，意为“排列，顺序”"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 range from延伸；（在一定范围内）变化"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 scope n. 范围"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 ranger n. 护林员"},{"type":"entry","text":"emerge /iˈmɜːrdʒ/ vi. 显露；（从隐蔽处）出现，出来","headword":"emerge"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 e（出）+merg（浸没）+e→从浸没之中出来→显露"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 emergence n. 显现；出现"}]},{"number":330,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"emergency n. 紧急情况，突发事件"},{"type":"entry","text":"split /splɪt/ v. 分开，分裂 n. 分裂","headword":"split"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 “死劈了它”→劈开→分开"},{"type":"entry","text":"lowland /ˈloʊlənd/ n. 低地","headword":"lowland"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 low（低的）+land（地）→低地"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 lowland lake低地湖"},{"type":"note","text":"反义 highland n. 高地"},{"type":"entry","text":"isolate /ˈaɪsəleɪt/ v. （使）隔离，（使）孤立","headword":"isolate"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 isol（=insul，岛屿）+ate（使…）→使成孤岛→使隔离，使"},{"type":"text","text":"孤立"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 isolate from 与…隔离"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 isolated a. 隔离的，孤立的"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"}]},{"number":331,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"常见鱼类："},{"type":"entry","text":"carp /kɑːrp/ n. 鲤鱼","headword":"carp"},{"type":"entry","text":"trout /traʊt/ n. 鳟鱼","headword":"trout"},{"type":"entry","text":"salmon /ˈsæmən/ n. 大马哈鱼，鲑鱼","headword":"salmon"},{"type":"entry","text":"tuna /ˈtuːnə/ n. 金枪鱼","headword":"tuna"},{"type":"entry","text":"sardine /ˌsɑːrˈdiːn/ n. 沙丁鱼","headword":"sardine"},{"type":"entry","text":"squid /skwɪd/ n. 鱿鱼","headword":"squid"},{"type":"entry","text":"sailfish /ˈseɪlˌfɪʃ/ n. 旗鱼","headword":"sailfish"},{"type":"entry","text":"mackerel /ˈmækrəl/ n. 鲭鱼","headword":"mackerel"},{"type":"entry","text":"billfish /ˈbɪlˌfɪʃ/ n. 长嘴鱼","headword":"billfish"},{"type":"entry","text":"marlin /ˈmɑːrlɪn/ n. 枪鱼","headword":"marlin"},{"type":"entry","text":"swordfish /ˈsɔːrdfɪʃ/ n. 剑鱼","headword":"swordfish"}]},{"number":332,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"octopus /ˈɑːktəpʊs/ n. 章鱼","headword":"octopus"},{"type":"text","text":"与“生物种群隔离”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"allopatric /ˌæloʊˈpætrɪk/ a. （生物学）分布在邻近不同地区的","headword":"allopatric"},{"type":"entry","text":"barrier /ˈbæriər/ n. 屏障；障碍","headword":"barrier"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 geographic barrier 地理障碍"},{"type":"entry","text":"canyon /ˈkænjən/ n. 峡谷","headword":"canyon"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 gorge n. 峡谷"},{"type":"text","text":"gully n. 溪谷"},{"type":"text","text":"ravine n. 峡谷，溪谷"},{"type":"text","text":"valley n.山谷"},{"type":"entry","text":"colonize /ˈkɑːlənaɪz/ vt. 移居于，大批生长于","headword":"colonize"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 来自colony（n. 殖民地；群体）"},{"type":"entry","text":"contact /ˈkɑːntækt/ n./v. 接触","headword":"contact"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 con（加强）＋tact（接触）→接触"},{"type":"entry","text":"coyote /kaɪˈoʊti/ n. 丛林狼","headword":"coyote"},{"type":"entry","text":"dispersion /dɪˈspɜːrʒn/ n. 分散；散布","headword":"dispersion"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 d